Lipstick review and swatches with my favourite lipstick shade💄 

I’ve tried a lot of lipsticks, but this one is next level! 🙌 The Mars Velvet Mousse Lipstick is a game-changer in my makeup routine. The moment you apply it, it feels like butter on your lips! It's smooth, lightweight, and gives that perfect matte finish.

One swipe and your lips are perfectly covered. The color payoff is insane, and it’s super buildable
You get high-end quality at such an affordable price point. Seriously, I’ve spent more on other brands that don’t even compare to the Mars Velvet Mousse. 😱
From nudes to bold reds, there’s a shade for every occasion. 

So, if you want lips that feel like velvet and look stunning all day long, grab your Mars Velvet Mousse Lipstick now. Trust me, you won’t regret it! 🙏💖

Isntree - Hyaluronic Acid Watery Sun Gel SPF50+ has been a delightful discovery. It's quickly become a strong contender for my holy grail, especially for daily wear.
This is where it truly shines. The "watery gel" description is spot on. It's incredibly lightweight, almost serum-like, and glides onto the skin effortlessly. There's absolutely no tugging or pulling, which is a huge plus for sensitive skin. It absorbs in seconds, leaving no sticky or greasy residue. Seriously, it feels like nothing is on your skin, which is a rare feat for an SPF50+ sunscreen. Reapplication throughout the day is also a breeze.

Looking for that perfect red that feels light as air? Let me put you on — it's not just a lipstick, it's a whole vibe!

This shade is a rich, deep red with just the right balance of bold and classy. What I love the most? It feels like nothing on the lips — super lightweight, mousse texture, and doesn’t dry me out like most matte lipsticks do.

It glides on smoothly, sets to a soft matte finish, and stays on comfortably for hours. Plus, it's multi-use — dab a little on your cheeks for a natural flush and you're good to go!

Perfect for festive looks, date nights, or even a bold everyday slay — this one is seriously underrated!
